<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10788</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16287</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布尔迪奥终于讲完了他的故事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16287</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>村民们离开了无花果树。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19787</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24288</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们挥舞着棍子和刀子冲向麦苏雅的小屋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24288</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们都带着火把。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要烧了巫师的小屋！”人们愤怒地大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>人群来到小屋，砸开了门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42288</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个人都以为麦苏雅和她丈夫被困在里面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42288</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，他们不在，只有一只凶猛的黑豹趴在床上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48787</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54714</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴希拉慢慢抬起头，尖利的白牙闪闪发光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54714</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57403</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>村民们尖叫起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57403</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60658</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他们害怕地跑到外面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60658</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们跑回自己的小屋，砰的一声关上了门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利从阴影中走出来，咧嘴笑着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74133</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个主意很好，巴希拉！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74133</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79675</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢。”黑豹自豪地边说边舔着自己的爪子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79675</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“天亮前，村民们不会出来的。我们现在休息一下吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91556</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当毛克利第二天醒来时，他看到了兰，那只老鹰。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91556</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95554</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我收到狼妈妈的消息了。”老鹰喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95554</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103554</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“麦苏雅和她丈夫在新村庄里很安全。村庄靠近沼泽地。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103554</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106801</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利高兴地挥了挥手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106801</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113552</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢！”然后，他去告诉巴希拉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113552</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118055</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴希拉说：“人们还躲在屋子内。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118055</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121557</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们为什么不忘掉他们，去打猎呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121557</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123963</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利摇了摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123963</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129153</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起，巴希拉。我必须完成我已经开始的事情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129153</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131323</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这是森林法则。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131323</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136403</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那些违反规则的人必须受到惩罚，记得吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136403</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴希拉耸了耸肩。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143154</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我在哪里能找到哈提？”毛克利问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143154</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147347</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哈提？”巴希拉说，“我不知道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147347</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他想去哪儿吃就去哪儿吃。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154053</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你能找到他，把他带到我这儿来吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157555</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴希拉困惑地看了毛克利一眼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157555</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不能命令森林之王。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163552</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“拜托了，巴希拉。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163552</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167554</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，毛克利想到了一个办法。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167554</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果哈提不来，你就说这些话：破坏田地。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177054</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>相信我，他会跟着你的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177054</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184304</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“破坏田地？”巴希拉重复着这句话，直到他记住了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184304</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189055</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他跑开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189055</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴希拉回来时，天已经黑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194840</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利松了一口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194840</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197636</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈提和巴希拉在一起。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197636</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大象的三个儿子跟在后面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205796</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你好，毛克利。”哈提喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205796</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利向这头老象行了个礼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他转向巴希拉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想给你讲一个关于一头聪明大象的故事。”毛克利说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴希拉看起来很惊讶，但他对毛克利点了点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有一次，这头大象被猎人的捕兽器抓住了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231155</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利看了一眼哈提。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231155</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在月光下，大家都能看到他侧身上有一道长长的白色疤痕。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244156</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>看起来好像有人用一根滚烫的鞭子打过他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244156</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249909</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“人们赶来要把他从捕兽器上弄出来。”毛克利继续说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249909</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但他很强壮，挣脱了绳子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259155</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他离开了，直到伤口痊愈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259155</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265153</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天晚上，他带领别的大象回来了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265153</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270154</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看着哈提。“接下来发生了什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270154</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272654</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哈提把故事讲完。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272654</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们踩了人类的田地。我们吃了他们的庄稼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们把房顶从他们小屋上掀了下来。然后......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286406</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他停了一下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286406</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290154</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们让野生森林进来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290154</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297564</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们让野生森林重新在村庄里生长起来，吞没了一切。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297564</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301219</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利满意地点了点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301219</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304469</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大象摇着鼻子看着他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>304469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你怎么知道这些田地被破坏了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>313727</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一天晚上，布尔迪奥讲了那个故事。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>313727</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>318402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利说，“我想他偶尔会说实话。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>318402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>323613</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你想从我这里得到什么？”哈提问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>323613</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>326887</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“住在这个村庄里的人很残忍。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>326887</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>332336</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利解释说，“他们伤害了麦苏雅和她的丈夫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>332336</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>334618</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们打算杀了我。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>334618</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>338869</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他们要用红花杀死麦苏雅。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>338869</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>342120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>只有惩罚他们才是对的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>342120</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>345868</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴希拉颤抖着放低了身子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>345868</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>351870</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在他明白毛克利为什么要找哈提了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>